  "an2.75:1.0": "75. Pleasures ",
  "an2.75:1.1": "“Monks, there are these two pleasures. ",
  "an2.75:1.2": "Which two? ",
  "an2.75:1.3": "Pleasure with enjoyment as its object & pleasure with equanimity as its object. ",
  "an2.75:1.4": "There are these two pleasures. ",
  "an2.75:1.5": "And the foremost of these two pleasures is pleasure with equanimity as its object.”",
